{"article_id":"E4M46xuIKdMNafnP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller has asked a grand jury in Washington , DC , to investigate Russia ' s meddling in the 2016 election ,","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"a major signal","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that the probe","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"into whether the Trump campaign colluded with Russia","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"is getting a whole lot bigger .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"As the Wall Street Journal reports ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"this means Mueller ' s probe has moved from simply investigating what might have happened","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to possibly charging people with crimes .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"That may not necessarily be an outcome , of course ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"but the fact","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that the investigation is widening","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"means there is more","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Mueller deems worth looking into .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The call for a grand jury is done for a specific purpose :","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"so that prosecutors can subpoena documents","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"they might not otherwise get ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"ensure","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"witnesses testify under oath ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"and formally charge someone with a crime","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"if they decide to .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"It ' s unlikely Mueller would have taken this step","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"unless he felt","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"there was a good reason","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to do so .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"And there is apparently good reason .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"CNN reports","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that the special counsel has found the financial ties between Trump associates and Russia to be among the most fruitful areas of investigation .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"There were signs","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"something like this was coming .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Since taking over the probe in May ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Mueller has hired 16 lawyers with expertise in multiple areas","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"including cybercrime , white-collar crime , and financial crime .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Clearly , his team is looking at all angles in this investigation .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"The move","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to involve a grand jury","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"implies","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"there is still much more","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to look into over the next few months .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"`` This is yet a further sign","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that there is a long-term , large-scale series of prosecutions","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"being contemplated","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and being pursued by the special counsel , ''","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Stephen Vladeck , a law professor at the University of Texas , told the Wall Street Journal .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"`` This suggests","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that the investigation is bigger and wider than Flynn , perhaps substantially so . ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Now , more than ever , the Trump-Russia story is not fake news .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"In fact , it just got very real .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"There ' s another problem for Trump besides the growing inquiry :","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"It ' s going to be much more difficult for him to fire Mueller .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"The more serious the investigation gets ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"the worse it looks for Trump to ask Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein to let Mueller go .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Rosenstein has said","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he would not fire Mueller","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"without \" good cause. \"","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"If Trump wanted to relieve Mueller of his duty now ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"it would show","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"he was reacting to the growing probe ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"as there is yet no indication of Mueller ineptly performing in his role .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Republicans have warned Trump","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that firing Mueller would be a bad idea .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"\" Any effort","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"to go after Mueller","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"could be the beginning of the end of the Trump presidency ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"unless Mueller did something wrong , \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"told NBC News .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"It remains to be seen how Trump will react to all of this .","depth":2},{"id":68,"text":"But the safe bet is he won ' t be happy about even more people looking into his finances , his friends , and his family .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":135,"right":136,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":113,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":95,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":88,"right":94,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":81,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":76,"right":80,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":1,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":5,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":8,"right":79,"relation"